name: Limited Edition Prints by Nelly Baksht

metadata.name: "ethEra and Terra", limited edition print #0005/8
metadata.description:
“This artwork is part of the “ethEra” series. Continue with the developing story of disruption and planetary evolution flowing forth from greater decentralization.”

Print on canvas 24″x30″

The number of prints is limited by 8.

Hand enhanced by artist – Each limited edition Giclee is hand embellished by the artist, making it one of a kind artwork. Signed and numbered – Each fine art limited edition is signed by the artist, certifying their inspection and approval, then numbered. Certificate of authenticity – Every limited edition Giclees painting includes a Certificate Of Authenticity signed by the artist. Exceptional longevity – Special varnish is an applied to give each Giclees a protective finish against UV light, moisture and scratches. Gallery display ready – Giclees are stretched on wood and not framed. The edges are painted so there is no need for additional framing. The artwork is ready for display. State-of-the-art reproduction -Our process is engineered for the fine art market. All of our Giclees have an elegant, vibrant full-color spectrum and maintain the look and feel of the original painting.
